  // GET /api/admin/branding - Get current branding (logo)
  // POST /api/admin/branding/logo - Update logo URL
  // ===== AI COST MONITORING ENDPOINTS (HQ Only) =====

  // GET /api/admin/ai-costs - Get AI usage cost aggregates
